name: TCC - Assistente Reflexivo
tagline: TCC Project of Ian and Jean
body:
### Welcome to GitHub Page of TCC - Assistente Reflexivo.
This page is about our Final Project to the Graduation in Computer System's Bachelor. You can branch our project using:

```
$ cd tcc/assistente-reflexivo
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

If you're using the GitHub for Mac, simply sync your repository and you'll see the new branch.

### Proposal
We propose to make a Android app that will analyse the development in self-learning of System Analyst and the Reflexible Analysis of them performance



### Authors and Contributors
@iancampelo and @jeansdp are the main Authors of the App. But we have a great contributor of @ferneda
